291
00:19:47,228 --> 00:19:48,363
Then go do your best.

292
00:19:53,038 --> 00:19:54,293
No, wait.

293
00:19:55,038 --> 00:19:56,563
That's Judge Kim's desk.

294
00:19:56,837 --> 00:19:58,403
