334
00:24:02,718 --> 00:24:04,712
Where are you from?

335
00:24:05,058 --> 00:24:06,553
We're from the Regional Investigation Unit.

336
00:24:16,927 --> 00:24:19,932
Did you install all the office equipment for the judges...

337
00:24:19,998 --> 00:24:22,502
